OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfsted promises changes    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter headteacher's death  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Schools watchdog Ofsted has said it    
OL,6, will make changes after the suicide of 
OL,7, headteacher Ruth Perry in January.     
OL,9,FChief Inspector Amanda Spielman said   
OL,10,FOfsted was piloting changes to its     
OL,11,Fcomplaints system, but added the single
OL,12,Foverall grade for schools would stay.  
OL,14,FMs Perry took her own life while       
OL,15,Fwaiting for Ofsted to publish a report 
OL,16,Fgrading her school Inadequate.         
OL,18,FHer sister Julia Waters told BBC News  
OL,19,Fshe wanted inspections to be paused, to
OL,20,Fallow a full review.                   
